headline: Arc Capital Partners and U.S. Realty Partners Announce the Recapitalization of Murrieta Town Center
summary: LOS ANGELES, January 07, 2026--Arc Capital Partners ("Arc"), an institutional real estate owner and investment manager focused on middle-market capital solutions, announced today that it has completed an investment in the recapitalization of Murrieta Town Center, a 380,000-square-foot, grocery-anchored retail center located in Murrieta, California. Arc partnered with U.S. Realty Partners ("U.S. Realty"), replacing the prior joint venture partner.
